name: MAIA_Reg_Browser
short_description: MAIA® Reg. Browser 1.4 helps you to browse the large number of registers in PIC® devices. You just have to pick up a register name in the Reg. List, and get all informations about the register: (Address(es), Bank(s), Configurations bits...). You can also use the search line to type the first letter of a register name or a configuration bit name (upper or lowercase). The software automatically pops up all the related register or configuration bit names beginning with the letter; So you just need to pick one and hit return to get all the necessary informations. Author: ANDRIAMILAMINA Monge.E-mail: mongemilamina@gmail.com. Web: https://www.andriamilamina.skyrock.com.
summary: MAIA® Reg. Browser 1.4 helps you to browse the registers of a PIC®
